_sText:
A field of sheds to hide in! Shame they aren't very durable. That's ok, there are some tunnels to hide in!

If you like this one, be sure to check out break_shedmines! Who knew one tweak to an idea could improve it so much?

UnRAR and drop the .bsp into your cstrike/maps folder. Enjoy! and leave feedback!

~Undies
